{"tid":433760,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[良心?錢太多?] 堅持不加價 IU機場開show最貴$1480","createTime":"2017-10-12T15:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T13:02:20.000Z","uid":34643,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"994e2d1335f3d85408473aa476d55352bd3b5bff","tid":433760,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T15:26:31.000Z","msg":"早前IU已宣佈會舉行巡唱，當中香港站「2017 IU Tour Concert &ldquo;Palette&rdquo; in Hong Kong」就會喺下月25號喺亞博館舉行，今次演唱會仲會係IU今次巡唱海外嘅唯一一站，足證IU好錫港迷。而之前IU來港開騷都會選唱廣東歌，不知今次佢又會唔會唱廣東歌？不過粉絲自然好奇到底香港場，GD會唔會又飛過來做嘉賓呢？<br />\n另外，IU香港站演唱會將於本月25號公開發售，門票分為$680、$1,080及$1,480三種。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171012/large/1507804325_80f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171012%2Flarge%2F1507804325_80f5.jpg&h=8370c772&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"443acba87d8801ea886fdf9d558caa76b3ab94b0","tid":433760,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T15:49:36.000Z","msg":"衰妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f623ab6a1519a439e14a743940fb8f6908399d9","tid":433760,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:10:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>衰妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.giphy.com/media/l0IsIm9kWDGZeO8BW/source.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fl0IsIm9kWDGZeO8BW%2Fsource.gif&h=3b4fc0ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe1fa3643ac7ec87b0ca79e7104af156b7d3cad1","tid":433760,"uid":43880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:25:47.000Z","msg":"年年張poster都好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968c00fcbdbf73f7e3554e75c8f02d49a6fd62cd","tid":433760,"